place_info.title: Siam Heritage, Massage & SPA treatments
place_info.address: 99 90 หมู่ที่ 1 ถนน ท้องศาลา, Ko Pha-ngan, Ko Pha-ngan District, Surat Thani 84280, Thailand

reviews.snippet: Ich würde nicht wieder kommen. Die Massage war eher durchschnittlich und nichts besonderes. Dafür war der Preis doppelt so teuer wie bei anderen Massage Studios. Am Anfang wurde Wasser serviert und am Ende Tee, das war gut. Der Laden an sich ist professionell und sehr sauber.
reviews.translated_snippet: I wouldn't come back. The massage was rather average and nothing special. However, the price was twice as high as at other massage studios. They served water at the beginning and tea at the end, which was good. The shop itself is professional and very clean.

response.snippet:
Dear Aleyna,
Thank you for taking the time to share your experience. 
We are sorry to hear that your visit did not fully meet your expectations.
At Siam Heritage, we are committed to providing a unique and high-quality experience.
Our operating costs are significantly higher than those of other establishments you may compare us to, and therefore, our prices reflect several elements that set us apart (even if they may not have been immediately noticeable to you). Here are a few examples:

• We use premium products, including high-quality oils with refined blends of Asian aromatic essences renowned for their therapeutic benefits.

• Our ergonomic equipment (such as thick futons for Thai massage or tables beds for oil massage with adjustable headrests, memory foam cushions, and heated overlays or such as very comfy reclined armchairs with an exclusive and immersive experience through the use of binaural music played via closed-back headphones) is specifically designed to maximize your comfort and your relaxation. 

• Our skilled and certified therapists undergo extensive and continuous training to ensure exceptional care and service.

That said, we are delighted to hear that you appreciated the warm welcome with cold infusion tea, and the snack offered after your treatment with hot tea, as well as the cleanliness of our facilities (hygiene is indeed a core focus for us and represents a considerable investment) and the professionalism of our team.

We sincerely hope to have the opportunity to welcome you again and allow you to discover more of the unique features of our expertise.

Kind regards,
Siam Heritage owner

reviews.snippet: We wanted to buy only one bag, then the employee offered us to buy socks with 20% discount. We took a pair of socks and after paying we noticed that no 20% discount was given.
